Notez:

Here is the latest full length Scooby Doo
original animated movie nice and early before
it comes out on DVD & BD on September 6!
For some reason Warner posted this streaming
via youtube in some new division of youtube
offering VOD. It had much more hefty protection
on the stream than the average youtube video.
Therefore the only way to get this done was
to screencap the film. The video quality
is quite exceptional for a screen cap if i do
say so myself. Audio is not the best ever, but its
definately not horrible. I simply reencoded the audio
& video to a more standard format, though please
note that without the hard work and effort of
my Scooby'riffic friend Shaggy this would never
even be here at all until it hits stores in 
september most likely! Sample included so u know
what the quality is like before grabbing the whole
film. Enjoy scooby fans!

P.S.
If anyone is somehow able to get their hands on the
source HD stream file that warnerVOD posted, please
get ahold of me and let me know. It would be greatly
appreciated!

P.P.S.
I know imdb lists this film as Attack Of the Phantosaur
but i think they are just not up to date, the dvd/BD
cover announced clearly say legend, as does the title
card in the film, so naturally thats the title i used.
Just wanted to point that out as the imdb link still lists
it as Attack as opposed to Legend!
